Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Printable
    Printable is a class that is an interface used in Customer and MainMenu
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Account
    Account class is an abstract class that is the parent of Checking, Savings and Credit classes.
    BankStatement
    Bank Statement class to print out bank statements
    Checking
    Checking class is the child class of Account and is used in Customer.
    Credit
    Credit class is the child class of Account and is used in Customer.
    Customer
    Customer class is child class of Person and implements Printable.
    MainMenu
    Main Menu class is a class that hold all menu functions to be used in the main RunBank file, implements Printable
    Person
    Person class is an abstract class that has a child class called Customer.
    RunBank
    This is the RunBank method where the main class it at utilizes MainMenu and Customer.
    Savings
    Savings class is child class of Account and is used in Customer.
